text.sw: 28. Uhusiano wa Mbadala wa Mkuu wa Kaya na Mkuu wa Kaya

text.default: 29. Who has signed the informed consent?
text.sw: 29. Ni nani aliyeweka saini fomu ya ridhaa?

text.default: (the boxes for both Household participation and Household head/Household head substitute participation must be signed)
text.pt: (As caixas de Participao do agregado familiar e Chefe/chefe substituto do agregado familiar tm de ser assinadas)
text.sw: (Lazima visanduku vya Ushiriki wa kaya na Mkuu wa kaya/Mbadala wa Mkuu wa kaya viwekwe saini)

text.default: 31a. Total number of houses (constructions) used to sleep in
text.pt: 31a. Nmero total de edificaes (construes) usados para dormir
text.sw: 31a. Jumla ya idadi ya nyumba (majengo) zinazotumika kulala

text.default: 32. Total number of rooms (compartments) used to sleep in
text.pt: 32. Nmero total de quartos (compartimentos) usados para dormir
text.sw: 32. Jumla ya idadi ya vyumba (vyumba vidogo) vinavyotumika kulala

text.default: 34. Wall material in the main house
text.pt: 34. Material da parede da edificao principal
text.sw: 34. Malighafi iliyojengea kuta za nyumba kuu

text.default: 35. Ceiling material in the main house
text.pt: 35. Material do teto da edificao principal
text.sw: 35. Malighafi iliyojengea paa la nyumba kuu

text.default: 36. Floor material in the main house
text.pt: 36. Material do cho da edificao principal
text.sw: 36. Malighafi iliyojengea sakafu ya nyumba kuu

text.default: 38a. [If answer to Q18 is other than Food is not cooked at home] Main energy source used for cooking:
text.pt: 38a. [Se a resposta  Q18 for diferente de Em casa no se cozinham alimentos] Energia principal utilizada para cozinhar:
text.sw: 38a. [Ikiwa jibu la Q18 ni lingine kando na "Chakula hakipikwi nyumbani] Chanzo kikuu cha nishati kinachotumika kupika:

text.default: 39. What is the main water source used for consumption (cooking and hygiene)?
text.pt: 39. Qual  a principal fonte de gua utilizada para consumo (cozinhar e higiene)?
text.sw: 39. Ni kipi chanzo kikuu cha maji yanayotumika kwa matumizi (kupika na usafi)?

text.default: 40. How much time does it take, in total, to reach the main water source, fetch water, and come back?
text.pt: 40.Quanto tempo demora, no total, a alcanar a principal fonte de gua, para ir buscar gua, e voltar?
text.sw: 40. Je, huchukua muda gani, kwa jumla, kufikia chanzo kikuu cha maji, kuchota maji na kurudi?

text.default: 41. Does the household possess a latrine?
text.pt: 41. Existe uma latrina no agregado familiar?

text.default: 41a. If there is no latrine in this household, where do the residents of this household defecate?
text.pt: 41a. Se no existir uma latrina neste agregado familiar, onde  que os habitantes deste agregado familiar defecam?
text.sw: 41a. Ikiwa hakuna choo katika kaya hii, wakazi wa kaya hii hujisaidia wapi?

text.default: 41b. Is the place where residents defecate close (<10m) to a water body?
text.pt: 41b. O lugar onde os habitantes deste agregado familiar defecam situa-se perto (<10 m) de uma massa de gua?
text.sw: 41b. Je, mahali ambapo wakazi huenda kujisaidi ni karibu (<mita10) na maji?

q41c.hint.text: You will be prompted to answer questions for the {{data.hh_how_many_latrines}} latrine(s)

text.default: 42. Main energy source used for household lighting
text.pt: 42. Principal fonte de energia utilizada na iluminao no agregado familiar
text.sw: 42. Chanzo kikuu cha nishati cha mwangaza wa kaya

text.default: 43. Does the household possess any of the following (mark all applicable):
text.pt: 43. O agregado familiar possuir qualquer um dos seguintes (assinalar todos os que se aplicam):
text.sw: 43. Je, kaya inamiliki chochote kati ya vitu vifuatavyo (weka alama kwa vyote vinavyo husika):

text.default: 44. Does the household currently own? (mark all that apply):
text.pt: 44. O agregado familiar possui atualmente? (Assinalar tudo o que se aplica):
text.sw: 44. Je, kaya yako kwa sasa inamiliki? (weka alama kwa vyote vinavyohusika):

text.default: 44a. How many of the following animals does the household possess?
text.pt: 44a. Quantos dos seguintes animais possui o agregado familiar?
text.sw: 44a. Je, kaya inamiliki wanyama wangapi kati ya wafuatao??

text.default: 44b. Does the household plan to own any cattle the coming year?
text.pt: 44b. O agregado familiar tenciona possuir bovino no prximo ano?
text.sw: 44b. Je, kaya ina mpango wa kumiliki ngombe yoyote mwaka unaokuja?

text.default: 44b. Does the household plan to own any pigs the coming year?
text.pt: 44b. O agregado familiar tenciona possuir porcos no prximo ano?
text.sw: 44b. Je, kaya ina mpango wa kumiliki nguruwe yoyote mwaka unaokuja?

text.default: 45. Where are the cattle housed at night?
text.pt: 45. Onde fica guardado os bovino durante a noite?

text.default: 45. Where are the pigs housed at night?
text.pt: 45. Onde fica guardado os porcos durante a noite?

text.default: 45c. If cattle are housed at night somewhere other than "inside the house where humans sleep", at what distance from the nearest structure where people are sleeping do they sleep?
text.pt: 45c. Se os bovino forem guardados  noite num stio diferente de dentro da casa onde dormem os seres humanos, a que distncia da estrutura mais prxima onde dormem as pessoas dormem esses animais?
text.sw: 45c. Ikiwa ngombe huifadhiwa nyakati za usiku mahali fulani tofauti na "ndani ambapo watu hulala", wao hulala umbali gani kutoka kwenye nyumba ambapo watu hulala?

text.default: 45c. If pigs are housed at night somewhere other than "inside the house where humans sleep", at what distance from the nearest structure where people are sleeping do they sleep?
text.pt: 45c. Se os porcos forem guardados  noite num stio diferente de dentro da casa onde dormem os seres humanos, a que distncia da estrutura mais prxima onde dormem as pessoas dormem esses animais?
text.sw: 45c. Ikiwa nguruwe huifadhiwa nyakati za usiku mahali fulani tofauti na "ndani ambapo watu hulala", wao hulala umbali gani kutoka kwenye nyumba ambapo watu hulala?

text.default: 46. Where do most weaned (no longer drinking milk from their mother) cattle spend the day during the wet season?
text.pt: 46. Onde  que a maioria dos animais desmamados (que j no bebem leite da progenitora) bovino passa o dia durante a estao das chuvas?
text.sw: 46. Ni wapi mara nyingi ndama ngombe (ambao hawanyonyi kutoka kwa mama yao) hukaa wakati wa msimu wa mvua?

text.default: 46. Where do most weaned (no longer drinking milk from their mother) pigs spend the day during the wet season?
text.pt: 46. Onde  que a maioria dos animais desmamados (que j no bebem leite da progenitora) porcos passa o dia durante a estao das chuvas?
text.sw: 46. Ni wapi mara nyingi ndama nguruwe (ambao hawanyonyi kutoka kwa mama yao) hukaa wakati wa msimu wa mvua?

text.default: 46a. [If confined] At what distance from the household is the structure?
text.pt: 46a. [Se confinados] A que distncia do agregado familiar se encontra a estrutura?
text.sw: 46a. [Ikiwa hufungiwa] Zizi hilo la mifugo lipo umbali gani kutoka kwenye kaya?

text.default: 46b. At what distance from the household do animals generally graze?
text.pt: 46b. A que distncia do agregado familiar pastam normalmente os animais?
text.sw: 46b. Kwa kawaida mifugo huenda malishoni umbali gani kutoka kwenye kaya?

text.default: 46c. Is there any type of standing water or flowing water in the animal grazing area during the wet season?
text.pt: 46c. Existe algum tipo de gua estagnada ou gua corrente na zona de pasto do animal durante a estao das chuvas?
text.sw: 46c. Kuna aina yoyote ya maji yaliyotuama au yanayotiririka katika eneo wanapolishwa wanyama msimu wa mvua?

text.default: 46c(i). [If yes] What is the type of water?
text.pt: 46c(i). [Se sim] Qual  o tipo de gua?
text.sw: 46c (i). [Ikiwa ndiyo] Maji haya ni ya aina gani?

text.default: 47. Did any of your cattle have any disease in the last 30 days? (check all that apply)
text.pt: 47. Os seus animais bovino tiveram alguma doena nos ltimos 30 dias? (Assinalar todas as opes que se apliquem)
text.sw: 47. Je, yeyote wa mifugo wako alikuwa na ugonjwa wowote katika siku 30 zilizopita? (weka alama kwa yote inayohusika)

text.default: 47. Did any of your pigs have any disease in the last 30 days? (check all that apply)
text.pt: 47. Os seus animais porcos tiveram alguma doena nos ltimos 30 dias? (Assinalar todas as opes que se apliquem)
text.sw: 47. Je, yeyote wa nguruwe wako alikuwa na ugonjwa wowote katika siku 30 zilizopita? (weka alama kwa yote inayohusika)

text.default: 48. If you dont currently own cattle, did you own cattle in the past 12 months
text.pt: 48. Se de momento no possui bovino, teve bovino nos ltimos 12 meses
text.sw: 48. Ikiwa kwa sasa humiliki ngombe, je, ulikuwa unamiliki ngombe katika miezi 12 iliyopita

text.default: 48. If you dont currently own pigs, did you own pigs in the past 12 months
text.pt: 48. Se de momento no possui porcos, teve porcos nos ltimos 12 meses
text.sw: 48. Ikiwa kwa sasa humiliki nguruwe, je, ulikuwa unamiliki nguruwe katika miezi 12 iliyopita

text.default: 49. In the past 12 months, have any of your cattle received ivermectin?
text.pt: 49. Nos ltimos 12 meses, foi administrada ivermectina a algum dos seus animais bovino?
text.sw: 49. Katika miezi 12 iliyopita, yoyote kati ya, ngombe wako alipokea ivamektini?

text.default: 49. In the past 12 months, have any of your pigs received ivermectin?
text.pt: 49. Nos ltimos 12 meses, foi administrada ivermectina a algum dos seus animais porcos?
text.sw: 49. Katika miezi 12 iliyopita, yoyote kati ya, nguruwe wako alipokea ivamektini?

text.default: 50. Who is responsible and makes the decisions about drug treatment of [cattle]
text.pt: 50. Quem  o responsvel e toma as decises sobre o tratamento do [bovino] com medicamentos?
text.sw: 50. Ni nani anayewajibika na anayefanya uamuzi kuhusu matibabu ya dawa ya [ngombe]

text.default: 50. Who is responsible and makes the decisions about drug treatment of [pigs]
text.pt: 50. Quem  o responsvel e toma as decises sobre o tratamento do [porcos] com medicamentos?
text.sw: 50. Ni nani anayewajibika na anayefanya uamuzi kuhusu matibabu ya dawa ya [nguruwe]

text.default: 51. In the past 12 months, did you send your cattle to slaughter?
text.pt: 51. Nos ltimos 12 meses, mandou bovino para abate?
text.sw: 51. Katika miezi 12 iliyopita, uliwapeleka ngombe kwenye machinjio?

text.default: 51. In the past 12 months, did you send your pigs to slaughter?
text.pt: 51. Nos ltimos 12 meses, mandou porcos para abate?
text.sw: 51. Katika miezi 12 iliyopita, uliwapeleka nguruwe kwenye machinjio?

text.default: 51a. In which months did you send your cattle to slaughter in the past 12 months? (check all that apply)
text.pt: 51a. Em que meses abateu o bovino nos ltimos 12 meses? (assinalar todas as opes que se apliquem)
text.sw: 51a. Ni katika mwezi upi ambapo uliwapeleka ngombe wako kwenye machinjio katika miezi 12 iliyopita? (weka alama kwa yote inayohusika)

text.default: 51a. In which months did you send your pigs to slaughter in the past 12 months? (check all that apply)
text.pt: 51a. Em que meses abateu o porcos nos ltimos 12 meses? (assinalar todas as opes que se apliquem)
text.sw: 51a. Ni katika mwezi upi ambapo uliwapeleka nguruwe wako kwenye machinjio katika miezi 12 iliyopita? (weka alama kwa yote inayohusika)

text.default: 52. In the past 12 months, did you milk your cows?
text.pt: 52. Nos ltimos 12 meses, ordenhou as suas vacas?
text.sw: 52. Katika miezi 12 iliyopita, uliwakamua maziwa ng'ombe wako?

text.default: 52a. [If yes] In which months do you normally milk your cows? (check all that apply)
text.pt: 52a. [Se sim] Em que meses normalmente ordenha as suas vacas? (Assinalar todas as opes que se apliquem)
text.sw: 52a. [Ikiwa ndiyo] Ni katika miezi ipi ambapo kwa kawaida huwa unakamua maziwa ng'ombe wako? (Chagua yote inayohusika)

text.default: 53. Are there any water bodies within the 50m surrounding the household buildings?
text.pt: 53. H corpos de gua num raio de 50 m  volta das edificaes do agregado familiar?
text.sw: 53. Je, kuna eneo la maji yoyote umbali ndani ya mita 50 yanayozunguka majengo ya kaya?

text.default: 54. Did the household receive indoors residual spraying for malaria in the past 12 months?
text.pt: 54. Foi feita pulverizao residual no agregado familiar contra a malria nos ltimos 12 meses?
text.sw: 54. Je, kaya ilipata kunyunyuziwa ndani viuatilifu ukoko kuzuia malaria katika miezi 12 iliyopita?

text.default: 54b. [If yes, ask to see the label] Was the spray registry label seen?
text.pt: 54b. [Se sim, pedir para ver a etiqueta Viu a etiqueta de registo da pulverizao?
text.sw: 54b. [Ikiwa ndiyo, omba kuona kibandiko] Je, kibandiko cha usajili wa kunyunyuzia dawa inaonekana?

text.default: 54b (i). [If label seen] Spray date (verify date on the fumigation registry label on the door)
text.pt: 54b (i). [Se viu a etiqueta Data da pulverizao (verificar data na etiqueta do registo de fumigao na porta)
text.sw: 54b (i). [Ikiwa kibandiko kinaonekana] Tarehe yakunyunyizia (Thibitisha tarehe kwenye kibandiko cha usajili wa unyunyiziaji kwenye mlango)

text.default: 55. How many mosquito nets are there in the household?
text.pt: 55. Quantas redes mosquiteiras existem no agregado familiar?
text.sw: 55. Je, kuna vyandarua vingapi vya mbu katika kaya hii?

text.default: 56. Are any other malaria prevention methods used? (click all that apply)
text.pt: 56. So usados outros mtodos de preveno da malria? (Assinalar todas as opes que se apliquem)
text.sw: 56. Kuna njia nyingine za kuzuia malaria zinazotumika? (chagua zote zinazotumika)

text.default: 57. What is the first point of formal health care used by the family when someone is sick?
text.pt: 57. Qual  o primeiro ponto de cuidados de sade formais usado pela famlia quando algum est doente?
text.sw: 57. Ni kituo kipi cha kwanza rasmi cha tiba ya afya kinachotumiwa na familia hii mtu anapokuwa mgonjwa?

text.default: (Formal care: health facility, community health worker (CHW), pharmacy, hospital)
text.pt: (Cuidados formais: unidade de sade, Agente Polivalente Elementar (APE), farmcia, hospital)
text.sw: (Tiba rasmi: kituo cha afya, Mhudumu wa afya wa jamii (CHW), duka la dawa, hospitali)

text.default: 58. Has any household member been bitten by a snake in the past 12 months?
text.pt: 58. Algum membro do agregado familiar foi mordido por uma cobra nos ltimos 12 meses?
text.sw: 58. Kuna mwanakaya yeyote aliyegongwa na nyoka katika miezi 12 iliyopita?

text.default: 58a. [If yes] How many household members were bitten in the past 12 months?
text.pt: 58a. [Se sim] Quantos membros do agregado familiar foram mordidos nos ltimos 12 meses?
text.sw: 58a. [Ikiwa ndiyo] Ni wanakaya wangapi waliyogongwa na nyoka katika miezi 12 iliyopita?

text.pt: 60. Nmero de contacto do agregado familiar

text.default: 62. Is there an alternative contact number 2
text.pt: 62. Existe um nmero de contacto alternativo 2
text.sw: 62. Je, kuna nambari ya 2 mbadala ya mawasiliano

text.default: 63. Can we call you on any one of the contact numbers indicated above to arrange visits with you in the context of this project?
text.pt: 63. Podemos ligar-lhe para qualquer um dos contactos indicados anteriormente para organizar visitas no contexto deste projeto?
text.sw: 63. Tunaweza kukupigia kupitia nambari yoyote ya mawasiliano kati ya zilizoonyeshwa hapo juu ili kupanga na wewe katika muktadha wa mradi huu?

text.default: 64. Have there been any deaths in the household in the past 12 months?
text.pt: 64. Houve algum bito no agregado familiar nos ltimos 12 meses?
text.sw: 64. Je, kumekuwa na vifo vyovyote katika kaya katika miezi 12 iliopita?
